{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Plan-review PASS (signed @ fb56f84fc, model claude-sonnet-4-6). Advisory triage:\n- f8613b5c (REBAR= for probe, validity 1.0): VALID — will run the smoke test as 'REBAR=$(pipx environment --value PIPX_BIN_DIR)/rebar bash scripts/probe-rebar.sh' so the probe targets the PUBLISHED pipx build, not the editable .venv (matches docs/releasing.md step 5).\n- f67e162c (mcp-publisher login/org-membership ordering, validity 1.0): VALID — will confirm navapbc public org membership BEFORE 'mcp-publisher login github', and re-login if membership is publicized after.\n- f2b56a07 (P9 file-impact missing): FIXED via set-file-impact (pyproject.toml, server.json).\n- fe85bddea (mcp-publisher version pin, validity 0.57): noted; docs/releasing.md doesn't pin it today — out of scope for this release, candidate doc follow-up.\n- fe72c9a4 (positive rationale, validity 0.57, minor): rationale is in docs/releasing.md ('PyPI is the base; Homebrew and the MCP Registry reference it'; OIDC trusted publishing avoids stored tokens). Not re-stating on the ticket."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782766355481037001,"uuid":"fc49db75-290b-45ae-a0e5-e4043904f839"}